    <section class="sg-block sg-section-helper-swappable-short-text-long-text-">
      <div class="sg-text">
        <h3 id="helper-swappable-short-text-long-text-" class="sg">HELPER - Swappable (short-text long-text)</h3>
        <p class="sg">
          <code class="sg">.swappable</code>- This pattern allows for responsive swapping of content from
          <code class="sg">.short-text</code>and
          <code class="sg">.long-text</code>. On the container element add
          <code class="sg">.swappable</code>and set the break point where you want it to switch by adding the class
          <code class="sg">.small</code>,
          <code class="sg">.medium</code>, or
          <code class="sg">.large</code>. The elements with the .short-text and .long-text must be inline elements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sg-example">
        <div class="sg-canvas">
          <h2 class="swappable medium">
            Swappable Sub-line
            <span class="sub-line">
              <span class="short-text">Short Title</span>
              <span class="long-text">Long TItle Seen on Medium Screens and Up</span>
            </span>
